The apartment has been reconstructed, with new riser pipes, a new core, and updated electrical wiring in the core. Monthly housing costs are approximately 150 € . The apartment comes with a cellar, and parking is public in front of the building. The housing cooperative is Bytterm. The entire apartment building is insulated with new elevators. The location of the apartment offers plenty of greenery, a park near the building, shops, restaurants, an elementary school, a high school, a university, and just a short walk to the public transport stop and much more. The price of the property is 132900 € . La distribución incluye un pasillo de entrada, una habitación más pequeña utilizada como cuarto de servicio, un salón, un dormitorio separado, una cocina y un baño con inodoro. El apartamento ha sido reformado, con nuevas tuberías principales, un núcleo nuevo y la electricidad actualizada en el núcleo. Los costos mensuales del hogar son aproximadamente 150 €.
